Anthony DOVE
v.
Debra SPELLER. No. 511P04. Supreme Court of North Carolina. April 6, 2005. David J. Fillippeli, Jr., Kinston, for Debra Speller.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 11th day of March 2005 by Plaintiff for "Petition for Rehearing":

"Motion Dismissed as moot by order of the Court In conference this the 6th day of April 2005."
